ui/manager/relations/relations_form.js :: RELATIONS FORM: `buildRelationsForm(container)` — builds the add/edit area for the Relations tab. Creates dual tag inputs (left/right), operator buttons (= > < =/=), swap button, search input, and add/cancel buttons. Returns `{ addArea, leftInput, rightInput, searchInput, addBtn, cancelBtn, ops, getSelectedOp, setSelectedOp, loadRuleIntoEditor }`.
ui/manager/relations/relations_list.js :: RELATIONS LIST: `buildRelationsList(container, formRefs)` — builds the searchable, sorted rule list for the Relations tab. Wires per-rule edit/duplicate/undo-able-delete actions. `formRefs` is the object returned by `buildRelationsForm`. Returns `{ list, renderRulesList }`.
ui/manager/relations/relations_page.js :: RELATIONS PAGE: `buildRelationsPage(container)` — orchestrates the Relations tab. Composes `buildRelationsForm` and `buildRelationsList`, wires the add/save flow and autocomplete on the left/right inputs.
